Challenges and Objectives

To enable proactive, data-driven healthcare at scale, our client partnered with us to address key operational and clinical challenges through an AI-powered real-time wellness platform.

Aggregate real-time vitals from multiple consumer wearables and medical sensors into one secure clinical data pipeline supporting continuous patient visibility across care environments.
Apply AI-driven trend analysis on streaming vitals to identify early risk signals, reduce false alerts, and enable clinicians to act before conditions escalate.
Present consolidated patient summaries, real-time trends, and prioritized alerts through intuitive dashboards designed to support faster clinical decision-making and workflow efficiency.
Design cloud-native infrastructure capable of handling millions of daily data points while maintaining low latency, high availability, and uninterrupted performance for large healthcare enterprises.
Enable seamless onboarding of diverse wearable brands and medical IoT devices without custom redevelopment, minimizing integration complexity and accelerating enterprise deployments at scale.
Enforce encryption, role-based access, audit logging, and secure cloud practices to ensure regulatory compliance and safeguard sensitive patient health data at the enterprise level.
